        </p><a
          href="/sign-up"
          class="mt-8 block w-full rounded-md bg-slate-900 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white"
          >Join as an Aventurer</a
        >
      </CardHeader>
    </Card>
    <div class="px-6 pb-8 pt-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-900">
        What's included
      </h3>
      <ul role="list" class="mt-4 space-y-3">
        <li class="flex space-x-3">
